      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your protective plates can better shield nearby allies.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.sqVVJqR60LM0lXIw]{Bulwark} species trait</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you use your bulwark species trait to grant an ally a bonus to AC, you grant a +5 bonus to AC against ranged attacks and a +1 bonus to Reflex saving throws when providing soft cover to allies until the beginning of your next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> Soft cover provides a +4 bonus to AC against ranged attacks and no bonus to Reflex saves.</p>"
